platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: 像1899年的人们那样画自画像

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 逼真银板效果 拍出复古肖像
Capture the soul of a portrait

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: This incredible filtering tool will have you looking old-timey in no time. Hipstamatic’s awesome app is truly like nothing we’ve ever seen, transforming portraits into photographs that look hundreds of years old. Plus, thanks to a Photos app extension, you can edit pics right from your library.
